      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 9.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>金玉滿堂，莫之能守；</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>When gold and jade fill the hall, their possessor cannot keep them safe.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
