      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 9.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>富貴而驕，自遺其咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>When wealth and honours lead to arrogancy, this brings its evil on itself.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
