      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 9.5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>功遂身退，天之道。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>When the work is done, and one's name is becoming distinguished, to withdraw into obscurity is the way of Heaven.</seg>
      </tuv>
